Remember with swings if I enter I will size for 60-70% loss, that’s just how option swings work but the goal is for 100%+ profits at first scale.

Keep an eye of the break & let’s see if we get an entry!

@everyone

Good morning team. No trades for me today as we are inside of yesterday’s range on ES/NQ and CPI is tomorrow. 

Based on my data, I don’t trade well prior to huge news event and after huge sell-offs. Big moves generally lead to some sort of consolidation. I could be wrong and there’s a big move today but I rather save my mental capital for more certain days. Professional athletes take rest days and I think traders should too. Trade safe see yall tomorrow
 @everyone
